# Project Structure

```
.
├── public/                        # Static assets (favicon, robots.txt)
├── src/
│   ├── components/
│   │   ├── layout/                # Navigation.tsx, Footer.tsx (site-wide)
│   │   ├── modules/               # Page section components (Hero, Pricing, etc.)
│   │   │   └── ModuleRenderer.tsx  # Switch that maps _type -> component
│   │   ├── ui/                    # shadcn primitives (button, card, sheet, etc.)
│   │   ├── PageModules.tsx        # Renders modules[] array
│   │   └── RevealObserver.tsx     # Intersection observer for scroll animations
│   ├── layouts/
│   │   └── Layout.astro           # Base HTML shell (head, VisualEditing, scripts)
│   ├── lib/
│   │   ├── utils.ts               # cn() helper for Tailwind class merging
│   │   └── icons.tsx              # Shared icon components
│   ├── pages/
│   │   ├── index.astro            # Root route, fetches page slug "home"
│   │   └── [[slug]].astro         # Optional catch-all for all other pages
│   ├── sanity/
│   │   ├── lib/
│   │   │   ├── load-query.ts      # Fetch wrapper (Visual Editing aware)
│   │   │   └── resolve.ts         # Presentation Tool location resolver
│   │   ├── queries.ts             # GROQ queries (defineQuery)
│   │   └── schemas/
│   │       ├── documents/         # page.ts, siteSettings.ts
│   │       ├── modules/           # hero.ts, pricing.ts, etc.
│   │       ├── objects/           # Reusable field groups (cta, seo, theme, etc.)
│   │       └── index.ts           # Barrel export of all schema types
│   ├── styles/
│   │   └── global.css             # Design tokens, Tailwind config, component classes
│   └── types/                     # Additional TS declarations
├── sanity.config.ts               # Studio config (structure, plugins, schema)
├── sanity.cli.ts                  # CLI config (TypeGen, schema extraction)
├── sanity.types.ts                # Generated types (do not edit)
├── schema.json                    # Extracted schema (do not edit)
├── astro.config.mjs               # Astro + Sanity + Cloudflare config
├── components.json                # shadcn config
└── wrangler.jsonc                 # Cloudflare Pages config
```

## Naming conventions

- Sanity schemas: `camelCase` filenames, one type per file (`hero.ts`, `pricingCard.ts`)
- React components: `PascalCase` filenames (`Hero.tsx`, `ModuleRenderer.tsx`)
- Astro pages: lowercase with brackets for params (`[[slug]].astro`)
- CSS: single `global.css` — no per-component CSS files
- Barrel exports: every schema subdirectory has an `index.ts`
